cp example-config.sh config.sh
# perhaps edit config.sh ... this allows the tests to work

to use this code as library components, check config.sh
for necessary environment variables.

the charset-conversion helper-program, marc8_to_utf8.pl, requires
that the MARC::Charset module be installed.  it is available here:
http://search.cpan.org/dist/MARC-Charset/

